{"tid":1035274,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人唔想追求d咩，純粹為屋企生存落去","createTime":"2019-02-24T13:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-26T11:39:00.000Z","uid":58316,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0b09557b28516961ebfce9836de262c5431ca4b7","tid":1035274,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T13:58:15.000Z","msg":"講真<br />\n做唔做人<br />\n冇所謂<br />\n來到世上<br />\n自己冇得揀<br />\n人大左<br />\n不知不覺<br />\n心淡到一個地步<br />\n唔再相信d咩<br />\n追求d咩<br />\n做d咩<br />\n都係哂氣<br />\n好憎讀書<br />\n為屋企而讀<br />\n細個個陣飛髮<br />\n長到成隻猩猩咁<br />\n屋企頂唔順<br />\n叫我去飛<br />\n先捨得飛<br />\n人大左<br />\n冇上進心<br />\n唔知上進黎做乜<br />\n叫我抽居屋<br />\nfine<br />\n但我真係可以<br />\n成世同老豆老母<br />\n屈係間公屋<br />\n叫我考入境海關<br />\n本身唔想<br />\n打份12k clerk<br />\n夠洗其實冇問題<br />\n紀律部隊又辛苦<br />\n本身冇操開<br />\n引體上升<br />\n一下都做唔到<br />\n算<br />\n可能真係聽話<br />\n人生在世<br />\n有幾可自己話事<br />\n自己捱<br />\n冇得揀<br />\n唔想黎到世上<br />\n都黎左<br />\n唯有唔好生仔<br />\n做人本身<br />\n就係苦<br />\n起碼做我個仔係"},{"pid":"7196b32a2f0422bb187e30f523763ad243fa613f","tid":1035274,"uid":180703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T14:03:26.000Z","msg":"考la, 唔搏唔升好R架炸"},{"pid":"2aa8bf82d0cc920525322c6e6461854e1284a7b6","tid":1035274,"uid":136038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T14:11:00.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n做<br />\n人<br />\n好<br />\n辛苦<br />\n好<br />\n想<br />\n放<br />\n棄<br />\n點解<br />\n冇<br />\n人<br />\n對<br />\n我好<br />\n當<br />\n我狗<br />\n咁撚<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc1296ec8749a375623b491549c19b59cc147250","tid":1035274,"uid":136625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T14:18:51.000Z","msg":"I know that feel bro, 又冇學歷又冇專長，一時無成，好彩啲叫做有個女朋友支持我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a9bd02b6fd1fe2aa60dc8014237d70c2f75d1b1","tid":1035274,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit